#accessibility","content":"**Tooltips**: Show on both hover and focus for keyboard users"},"1114":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-146","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#rendering-strategy","content":"The component uses VisX primitives for optimal SVG rendering:"},"1115":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-147","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#rendering-strategy","content":"**Scales**: VisX's `scaleBand` and `scaleLinear` for efficient coordinate mapping"},"1116":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-148","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#rendering-strategy","content":"**Grouped rendering**: Bars are rendered in SVG `<Group>` elements for logical organization"},"1117":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-149","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#rendering-strategy","content":"**Responsive sizing**: `useParentSize` hook provides efficient resize detection with debouncing (15ms)"},"1118":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-150","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#scrolling-strategy","content":"**Vertical charts**: Horizontal scrolling when many data points exceed container width"},"1119":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-151","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#scrolling-strategy","content":"**Horizontal charts**: Vertical scrolling when many categories exceed container height"},"1120":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-152","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#scrolling-strategy","content":"**Sticky axes**: Positioned absolutely t